<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>ESSAY | LAST &amp; GABA</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #FAF9F6;
        --text: #333333;
        --accent: #999;
        --font-serif: "YuMincho", "Yu Mincho", serif;
        --font-sans: "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN",
          "Hiragino Sans", sans-serif;
      }

      body {
        background-color: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
        margin: 0;
        padding-top: 80px;
        overflow-x: hidden;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      header.top-bar {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 80px;
        background-color: var(--bg);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        padding: 0 40px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        z-index: 3000;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        gap: 24px;
      }

      .menu-trigger {
        width: 28px;
        height: 18px;
        cursor: pointer;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }
      .menu-trigger span {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        height: 2px;
        background-color: #333;
        transition: 0.3s;
      }

      .header-logo {
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.4em;
        cursor: pointer;
        color: var(--text);
        text-decoration: none;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .menu-overlay {
        position: fixed;
        inset: 0;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
        opacity: 0;
        pointer-events: none;
        transition: opacity 0.25s ease;
        z-index: 3200;
      }
      .menu-overlay.is-open {
        opacity: 1;
        pointer-events: auto;
      }

      .menu-panel {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 320px;
        max-width: 80vw;
        height: 100%;
        background: #111;
        color: #f5f5f5;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        padding: 32px 40px;
        transform: translateX(-100%);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      }
      .menu-overlay.is-open .menu-panel {
        transform: translateX(0);
      }

      .menu-close {
        font-size: 24px;
        line-height: 1;
        cursor: pointer;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }

      .menu-title {
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.4em;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }

      .menu-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .menu-item {
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .menu-line {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: baseline;
        gap: 0.6em;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
      }

      .menu-number {
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        color: var(--accent);
      }
      .menu-label {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      }

      .brand-tree {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 6px 0 0 1.9em;
        margin: 0;
        display: none;
      }
      .brand-tree.is-open {
        display: block;
      }
      .brand-tree li {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: #ccc;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      }
      .brand-tree a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .brand-tree a:hover {
        color: #fff;
      }

      main {
        padding: 40px 5vw;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .description {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 900px;
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        line-height: 2.2;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: #444;
        text-align: left;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        header.top-bar {
          padding: 0 20px;
          height: 60px;
          gap: 16px;
        }
        body {
          padding-top: 60px;
        }

        .menu-panel {
          width: 240px;
          padding: 20px 16px;
        }

        .menu-title {
          font-size: 1.1rem;
          letter-spacing: 0.3em;
          margin-bottom: 22px;
        }

        .menu-number {
          font-size: 0.75rem;
        }

        .menu-label {
          font-size: 1rem;
          letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        }

        .brand-tree li {
          font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        main {
          padding: 28px 16px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="top-bar">
      <div class="menu-trigger" id="menuBtn">
        <span></span><span></span><span></span>
      </div>
      <a href="/" class="header-logo">LAST &amp; GABA</a>
    </header>

    <div class="menu-overlay" id="menuOverlay">
      <div class="menu-panel">
        <div class="menu-close" id="menuClose">×</div>

        <div class="menu-title">LAST &amp; GABA</div>

        <ul class="menu-list">
          <li class="menu-item">
            <a class="menu-line" href="/elements">
              <span class="menu-number">01</span>
              <span class="menu-label">ELEMENTS</span>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="menu-item">
            <a class="menu-line" href="/progress">
              <span class="menu-number">02</span>
              <span class="menu-label">PROGRESS</span>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="menu-item">
            <a class="menu-line" href="/essay">
              <span class="menu-number">03</span>
              <span class="menu-label">ESSAY</span>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="menu-item">
            <span class="menu-line" id="brandsToggle">
              <span class="menu-number">04</span>
              <span class="menu-label">BRANDS</span>
            </span>
            <ul id="brandList" class="brand-tree">
              <li><a href="/brands/comoli">COMOLI</a></li>
              <li><a href="/brands/ssstein">SSSTEIN</a></li>
              <li><a href="/brands/forme">FORME</a></li>
              <li><a href="/brands/manifold">MANIFOLD</a></li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <main>
      <!-- メイン画像 -->
      <div
        style="
          width: 100%;
          max-width: 900px;
          margin: 0 auto 40px auto;
          text-align: center;
        "
      >
  <img
    src="/essay/forest-0001.jpg"
    alt="森の風景"
    style="
      width: 100%;        /* ここを 100% にして親要素いっぱいまで広げる */
      max-width: 720px;   /* 画像自体の最大横幅。お好みで 640 / 720 / 800 など */
      height: 460px;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto;
    "
  />      </div>

      <!-- エッセイ本文 -->
      <div class="description">
        <section>
          <h2 style="margin-bottom: 0.5em;">
            <span style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #999; margin-right: 0.75em;">
              ESSAY 0001
            </span>
            <span style="font-size: 1.1rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em;">
              森の写真について（仮タイトル）
            </span>
          </h2>

          <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5em; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #777;">
            2026 / LOCATION / NOTE
          </p>

          <p>
            ここに日本語のテキストを書いてください。森の湿度、音の少なさ、
            自分が着ていた服のこと、このあと何をしに行ったのか──自由に書いてOKです。
          </p>

          <p>
            満足いく1本が書けたら、この &lt;section&gt; 全体をコピーして、
            ESSAY 0002 としてタイトルや本文だけ差し替えていけば、エッセイを増やしていけます。
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>

    <script is:raw>
      document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
        const menuBtn = document.getElementById('menuBtn');
        const menuOverlay = document.getElementById('menuOverlay');
        const menuClose = document.getElementById('menuClose');
        const brandsToggle = document.getElementById('brandsToggle');
        const brandList = document.getElementById('brandList');

        const openMenu = () => {
          menuOverlay.classList.add('is-open');
        };
        const closeMenu = () => {
          menuOverlay.classList.remove('is-open');
        };

        menuBtn?.addEventListener('click', openMenu);
        menuClose?.addEventListener('click', closeMenu);
        menuOverlay?.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
          if (e.target === menuOverlay) closeMenu();
        });

        brandsToggle?.addEventListener('click', () => {
          brandList?.classList.toggle('is-open');
        });
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>